_______________________________________________________________________________
"Psionic Profile"  
        A psionicist with psionic profile can alter his "psychic
        signature" to other psionicists.  It simply allows him to change
        his guild level title displayed in the guild who list.  Much
        more interesting than simply being known as "a Psionicist."
 
SP Cost:  10		Guild Level:  2		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  profile <new description>
